  <summary>3/19/1998--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase standard deduction amounts. Establishes the deduction for a joint return or surviving spouse at twice that for: (1) an individual who is not married and not a surviving spouse or head of household; or (2) a married individual filing separately. Provides for annual inflation adjustments.</summary>
